.product
    .container
        .row.space-between
            .product__images
                .product__image.product__image_lg
                    img(src='image/product.png' width="100%")

                .row.space-between
                    .product__image.product__image_sm
                        img(src='image/product.png' width="100%")

                    .product__image.product__image_sm
                        img(src='image/product.png' width="100%")

                    .product__image.product__image_sm
                        img(src='image/product.png' width="100%")


            .product__info
                .row.space-between
                    .product__name Biker hoodie
                    .product__price $24.00

                .product__description.
                    Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Architecto aspernatur at consectetur cum cupiditate dolores doloribus exercitationem explicabo fuga fugiat ipsum iusto, labore natus nisi tempore, tenetur ullam ut veniam!

